claim.claim-text:
1. A wireless telephone communication system for a set top box, comprising: 
(A)a base unit connected to an AC power line for the transmission and receipt of control and data signals; 
(B)an extension unit connected to an AC power line for the transmission and receipt of control and data signals to and from said base unit; 
(C)a set top box connected to said extension unit; and 
(D)a central office device connected to said base unit.
